 121:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Enable or disable peripheral illegal access detection with HAL_RIF_IAC_EnableIT /
 122:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****         HAL_RIF_IAC_DisableIT.
 123:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rif.c ****     (#) Retrieve an illegal access flag from a designated peripheral with HAL_RIF_IAC_GetFlag
